{"tid":694522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警破虛擬貨幣投資騙案　拘8人涉款5800萬","createTime":"2018-06-08T11:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T17:19:03.000Z","uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"36a0b9b1a4e6b5121f9096ccf35a09c97565f9b0","tid":694522,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"是咪連登之前講果單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n06月08日(五)<br />\n17:49更新<br />\n15:58建立<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180608/bkn-20180608155827698-0608_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180608%2Fbkn-20180608155827698-0608_00822_001.html&d=TP16uof%2BsUC64KvAjN0iLIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e7363a22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180608/bkn-20180608155827698-0608_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n警方西九龍總區重案組偵破一宗牽涉虛擬貨幣的投資騙案，據知涉款高達5800萬港元，8人涉嫌「欺詐」落網。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被捕8人中有3名為本地人，其餘為馬來西亞人，而目前向警方求助的受害人約有116人，當中30名為本地人，其餘大部分來自內地。消息指，被捕人開設投資公司，推銷客人投資一種虛擬貨幣，受害人經公司將美元轉換成該種貨幣後，再下載手機應用程式一直留意其價格，據知期間貨幣價格不斷上升。其後，受害人發現該手機應用程式突然停止運作，所投資的資金未能取回，懷疑受騙，本月初集體報警。"},{"pid":"0d3f4e636aa64a10258b8faccc197dffbc914b1b","tid":694522,"uid":71748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"火x 森？"},{"pid":"94cf733d7306e50f7b917e8b349f4424bde835c1","tid":694522,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"x燎森？"},{"pid":"f57406696d622b82843a4b3a1c59b30c543086c5","tid":694522,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62942e635d6f57c078d32d5afc191c19e07df658","tid":694522,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:18:11.000Z","msg":"無支那背景"},{"pid":"67e72cc7197b4a3b82ad60844c3e863b947f2e08","tid":694522,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"火燎x?"},{"pid":"9e4f1fdef6aa2a00ce31108aafa115d2cb71dccf","tid":694522,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"幣少爺？"},{"pid":"0ef873e6d01a8f0b466b856e16c6cd6a46864672","tid":694522,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd17668d1ad6726cebc8f91aa320616dffef42f9","tid":694522,"uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識又跟人玩coin"},{"pid":"db87b3686f4ca61eea32520380162c6faeaf3ff4","tid":694522,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識又跟人玩coin</blockquote><br />\n都唔可以叫唔識，比人騙者。"},{"pid":"9caa38fa33afed0055998151b151af7f5ce7477e","tid":694522,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:19:03.000Z","msg":"果條火乜撚？"}]}